dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line shapefile contains bicycle lanes, paths, and routes within the 9 counties of the San Francisco Bay Area in California. Data are current as of May 19, 2006. This layer is part of the Bay Area Metropolitan Transportation Commission (MTC) GIS Maps and Data collection.
